{"id":310,"date":"2024-10-29T14:22:19","date_gmt":"2024-10-29T14:22:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/?page_id=310"},"modified":"2024-12-02T07:03:52","modified_gmt":"2024-12-02T07:03:52","slug":"travel","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/travel","title":{"rendered":"Travel"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-bottom:0;padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20)\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-77288cabcbc41d4d4b596ede60c5e2a4\" style=\"color:#325db9\">About Mainz<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Mainz, the capital of Rhineland-Palatinate, is one of the oldest cities in Germany and is picturesquely situated on the banks of the Rhine.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-details has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-details-is-layout-flow\" style=\"background-color:#888eba12\"><summary>More information &#8230;<\/summary>\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div style=\"height:117px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-right\">Founded by the Romans, the city&#8217;s long history is reflected in many of its buildings and attractions. Mainz is best known as the home of Johannes Gutenberg, inventor of the printing press, whose legacy is honored in the Gutenberg Museum. The imposing Mainz Cathedral, a masterpiece of Romanesque architecture, dominates the cityscape and is one of its landmarks.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:82px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"579\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Augustingerkirche_Pixabay-579x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3253\" style=\"width:460px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Augustingerkirche_Pixabay-579x1024.jpg 579w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Augustingerkirche_Pixabay-170x300.jpg 170w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Augustingerkirche_Pixabay-768x1358.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Augustingerkirche_Pixabay-869x1536.jpg 869w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Augustingerkirche_Pixabay-rotated.jpg 1086w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 579px) 100vw, 579px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Photo: <a href=\"https:\/\/pixabay.com\/de\/users\/wikimediaimages-1185597\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\">WikimediaImages<\/mark><\/a> via <a href=\"https:\/\/pixabay.com\/de\/photos\/augustinerkirche-mainz-au%C3%9Fen-855531\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\">Pixabay<\/mark><\/a><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignright size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"576\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Dom_Pixyabay-576x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3250\" style=\"width:455px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Dom_Pixyabay-576x1024.jpg 576w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Dom_Pixyabay-169x300.jpg 169w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Dom_Pixyabay-768x1365.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Dom_Pixyabay-864x1536.jpg 864w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Dom_Pixyabay-rotated.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Photo: <a href=\"https:\/\/pixabay.com\/de\/users\/lapping-3464230\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\">lapping<\/mark><\/a> via <a href=\"https:\/\/pixabay.com\/de\/photos\/mainzer-dom-mainz-rheinland-pfalz-2322626\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\">Pixabay<\/mark><\/a><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:116px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>The beautiful old town with its half-timbered houses, the Augustinian Church and the Romano-Germanic Central Museum are also worth a visit. Those interested in culture will appreciate the State Theater and the annual \u201cMainzer Johannesfest\u201d (in June).<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<div style=\"height:130px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-right\">The area around Mainz also has a lot to offer: Rheinhessen and Rheingau wine regions are known for their excellent wines, and along the Rhine, charming wine villages such as R\u00fcdesheim or the castles of the Middle Rhine Valley invite you to take a trip. Wiesbaden, the state capital of Hessen, is just across the river, and the proximity to Frankfurt makes Mainz an ideal base for those who love skyscrapers and big city life.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Rudesheim_Pixabay-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3259\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Rudesheim_Pixabay-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Rudesheim_Pixabay-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Rudesheim_Pixabay-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Rudesheim_Pixabay-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Rudesheim_Pixabay.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Photo: <a href=\"https:\/\/pixabay.com\/de\/users\/jonny_joka-4913008\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\">Jonny_Joka<\/mark><\/a> via <a href=\"https:\/\/pixabay.com\/de\/photos\/r%C3%BCdesheim-stadt-dorf-fluss-6368588\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\">Pixabay<\/mark><\/a><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-8709ead995d494b41ec2e50a310f98b0\" style=\"color:#325db9\">List of top attractions in Mainz:<br><\/h5>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"574\" src=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/MainzInnenstadt_Pixabay-1024x574.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3262\" style=\"width:738px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/MainzInnenstadt_Pixabay-1024x574.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/MainzInnenstadt_Pixabay-300x168.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/MainzInnenstadt_Pixabay-768x430.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/MainzInnenstadt_Pixabay-1536x861.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/MainzInnenstadt_Pixabay.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Photo: <a href=\"https:\/\/pixabay.com\/de\/users\/lapping-3464230\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\">lapping<\/mark><\/a> via <a href=\"https:\/\/pixabay.com\/de\/photos\/mainz-rheinland-pfalz-deutschland-2333762\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\">Pixabay<\/mark><\/a><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"578\" src=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Brucke-2-1024x578.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3265\" style=\"width:740px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Brucke-2-1024x578.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Brucke-2-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Brucke-2-768x433.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Brucke-2-1536x866.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Brucke-2.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Photo: Organizing Committee ECVP 2025<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<div style=\"height:78px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<ol style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);margin-bottom:0;margin-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0\" class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10)\">Mainz Cathedral (St. Martin&#8217;s Cathedral): An impressive example of Romanesque architecture, the city&#8217;s landmark. The cathedral is over 1,000 years old and offers a fascinating insight into the history of the region.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10)\">Mainz Old Town: The picturesque Old Town of Mainz with its narrow streets, half-timbered houses and cozy squares invites you to take a stroll. The Augustinian Church and the Kirschgarten quarter are especially worth seeing.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Roman-Germanic Central Museum: An important archaeological museum with finds from Roman and Germanic history. There are exciting exhibitions about life in Roman times.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10)\">Mainz Carnival Fountain: An ornate fountain on Schillerplatz that symbolizes the centuries-old Mainz carnival. It is a popular attraction during the carnival season.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Rhine promenade: The Rhine promenade is a beautiful place to walk, bike or just relax. Many events take place here, especially in summer.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-91352f4ccb0d412f7427b72e0af1bbe6\" style=\"color:#325db9\">Places to visit around Mainz:<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<ol style=\"margin-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);margin-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10)\" class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Kurhaus (Wiesbaden): A grand historic spa and entertainment complex, known for its stunning architecture and lush surrounding gardens. Built in the mid-19th century, it has served as a symbol of the city&#8217;s rich thermal bath heritage and is a popular venue for concerts, events, and conventions.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10)\">Rheingau and Eberbach Abbey: One of Germany&#8217;s most famous wine regions. Eberbach Abbey, a former Cistercian monastery, has beautiful architecture and is famous as a filming location for \u201cThe Name of the Rose\u201d.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Middle Rhine Valley and Loreley: A UNESCO World Heritage Site with spectacular castles and palaces along the Rhine. The Loreley, a famous rock, is particularly picturesque.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10)\">R\u00fcdesheim on the Rhine: A charming wine town in the Rheingau, famous for the Drosselgasse, wine tasting and the Niederwalddenkmal with panoramic views over the Rhine.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Frankfurt am Main: A vibrant metropolis known for its striking skyline, Frankfurt combines modern architecture with rich history, offering top attractions, as well as a vibrant nightlife.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignright size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"578\" src=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/KurhausWiesbaden_Pixabay-1024x578.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3268\" style=\"width:725px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/KurhausWiesbaden_Pixabay-1024x578.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/KurhausWiesbaden_Pixabay-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/KurhausWiesbaden_Pixabay-768x433.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/KurhausWiesbaden_Pixabay-1536x866.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/KurhausWiesbaden_Pixabay.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Photo: <a href=\"https:\/\/pixabay.com\/de\/users\/lapping-3464230\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\">lapping<\/mark><\/a> via <a href=\"https:\/\/pixabay.com\/de\/photos\/kurhaus-wiesbaden-hessen-2352996\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\">Pixabay<\/mark><\/a><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignright size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Frankfurt-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3271\" style=\"width:726px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Frankfurt-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Frankfurt-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Frankfurt-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Frankfurt-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Frankfurt.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Photo: Organizing Committee ECVP 2025<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you want to know more about Mainz? Visit the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.mainz.de\/en\/index.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#ef767a\" class=\"has-inline-color\">city homepage<\/mark><\/a> for more information.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Clicking on the image below will take you to our <a href=\"https:\/\/umap.openstreetmap.de\/de\/map\/ecvp-2025_74049?scaleControl=false&amp;miniMap=false&amp;scrollWheelZoom=true&amp;zoomControl=true&amp;editMode=disabled&amp;moreControl=true&amp;searchControl=null&amp;tilelayersControl=null&amp;embedControl=null&amp;datalayersControl=true&amp;onLoadPanel=caption&amp;captionBar=false&amp;captionMenus=true&amp;datalayers=5b71272a-d095-47d7-9b0b-bbc477da1e18#11\/50.1124\/8.1470\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https:\/\/umap.openstreetmap.de\/de\/map\/ecvp-2025_74049?scaleControl=false&amp;miniMap=false&amp;scrollWheelZoom=true&amp;zoomControl=true&amp;editMode=disabled&amp;moreControl=true&amp;searchControl=null&amp;tilelayersControl=null&amp;embedControl=null&amp;datalayersControl=true&amp;onLoadPanel=caption&amp;captionBar=false&amp;captionMenus=true&amp;datalayers=5b71272a-